creator: MealPal, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
MealPal gives you access to the best food near you, for just $5.99 per meal.


From salads and sushi to spaghetti and sandwiches, choose and pick up delicious meals from hundreds of local restaurants with just a few taps.


How does it work?


Reserve

Discover new restaurants and select your weekday lunch (or dinner) with easy-to-use filters and a hyper-local map.


Pick Up

Arrive at the restaurant and head straight to the cashier - skipping the line never felt so good!


Rate

Enjoyed the food? Lettuce know and we’ll serve up recommendations that we think you’ll love.


MealPal is available in Auckland, Austin, Boston, Brooklyn, Chicago, Denver, London, Los Angeles, Manchester, Melbourne, Miami, New York City, Philadelphia, Portland, San Francisco, Seattle, Singapore, Sydney, Toronto, Washington, D.C., and Wellington -- plus,
more coming soon!

title: MealPal

creator: MealPal, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
With a MealPal membership, you get lunch from hundreds of local restaurants for less than £5 per meal! Download the MealPal app to request an invite, or log in with your existing account to reserve your lunch.

-- EASY ORDERING --

Starting at 17:00 the night before until 09:30 the morning of, reserve your lunch by selecting a meal from a restaurant near you. Use a map view for easy navigation, or sort your options in a list. Tap the meal that looks most appetizing, choose a pickup window, and you’re all set!

-- MEET PAL, YOUR FAVORITE LUNCH BUDDY --

Vegetarian? In the mood for Italian? Or just looking for something light to munch on? Use Pal’s filters to find the perfect dishes for you. And if you love what you ordered, tap the heart icon on your meal to add the restaurant to your favorites.

MealPal is available in Boston, Chicago, Miami, New York City, Philadelphia, San Francisco, Washington, DC, and London, but we’re just getting started. Check back for updates to see if we’re in your city next!

title: MealPal

creator: MealPal, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
With a MealPal membership, you get lunch from hundreds of local restaurants for less than £5 per meal! Download the MealPal app to request an invite, or log in with your existing account to reserve your lunch.

-- EASY ORDERING --

Starting at 17:00 the night before until 09:30 the morning of, reserve your lunch by selecting a meal from a restaurant near you. Use a map view for easy navigation, or sort your options in a list. Tap the meal that looks most appetizing, choose a pickup window, and you’re all set!

-- MEET PAL, YOUR FAVORITE LUNCH BUDDY --

Vegetarian? In the mood for Italian? Or just looking for something light to munch on? Use Pal’s filters to find the perfect dishes for you. And if you love what you ordered, tap the heart icon on your meal to add the restaurant to your favorites.

MealPal is available in Boston, Chicago, Miami, New York City, Philadelphia, San Francisco, Washington, DC, and London, but we’re just getting started. Check back for updates to see if we’re in your city next!

title: MealPal

creator: MealPal, Inc.
descriptionHtml:
MealPal gives you access to the best food near you, for just $5.99 per meal.


From salads and sushi to spaghetti and sandwiches, choose and pick up delicious meals from hundreds of local restaurants with just a few taps.


How does it work?


Reserve

Discover new restaurants and select your weekday lunch (or dinner) with easy-to-use filters and a hyper-local map.


Pick Up

Arrive at the restaurant and head straight to the cashier - skipping the line never felt so good!


Rate

Enjoyed the food? Lettuce know and we’ll serve up recommendations that we think you’ll love.


MealPal is available in Auckland, Austin, Boston, Brooklyn, Chicago, Denver, London, Los Angeles, Manchester, Melbourne, Miami, New York City, Philadelphia, Portland, San Francisco, Seattle, Singapore, Sydney, Toronto, Washington, D.C., and Wellington -- plus,
more coming soon!
